  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This Phase 2 study is a 3-site, double-blind, randomised, placebo-controlled, 3-way
      cross-over trial, involving 3 treatments with Modafinil 300 mg or the combination drug THN102
      (Modafinil/Flecainide 300 /3 mg, Modafinil/Flecainide 300 /27 mg).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The 3 double blind periods (2-week) follow a stabilisation period for modafinil at 300 mg/day
      (open, 2-week) and are followed by a one-week washout period with the same modafinil dose.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
